---

This skill bundles the following third-party libraries; each retains its own
license, preserved in the asset file's own header:

- marked v12.0.2 (MIT) — https://github.com/markedjs/marked
- highlight.js v11.9.0 (BSD-3-Clause) — https://github.com/highlightjs/highlight.js
- Primer Octicons (MIT) — https://github.com/primer/octicons
  (Individual SVG paths are inlined into skills/why/assets/report_template.html.)

The skill composes Gravatar URLs (https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/<md5>) from
git author emails; Gravatar images themselves are served by gravatar.com and
are not bundled.
